title: BRIEF-SZZT Electronics gets regulatory approval to issue up to 400 mln yuan bonds
text:
Sept 8 SZZT Electronics Co Ltd
* Says gets securities regulator's approval to issue up to 400 million yuan ($62.84 million) bonds
